--data binding
    process of converting JSON to Java Object and Java Object to JSON
    data binding is also called marshalling/de marshalling serialization / deserialization
    jackson is used for data binding

 --rest api design
    use plural name of entity in api url
    don't use verb in uri, use http methods instead of that
    POST: /api/employees  - create a new employee
    GET: /api/employees - Read a list of employees
    GET: /api/employees/{employeeId} - Read a single employee
    PUT: /api/employees   - update an existing employee
    DELETE: /api/employees/{employeeId} - Delete an existing employee